{
  "video_id": "qS7mBbXxJYA",
  "title": "I grew up in a cult. It was heaven -- and hell. | Lilia Tarawa | TEDxChristchurch",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Thành H. Châu Reviewer: Peter van de Ven"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 13759.0,
      "end_time": 15109.0,
      "text": "I grew up in a valley"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 15109.0,
      "end_time": 17779.0,
      "text": "on the West coast of New Zealand&#39;s South Island."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 18520.0,
      "end_time": 23209.0,
      "text": "Imagine the wildest, most beautiful valley you&#39;ve ever seen."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23598.0,
      "end_time": 27997.0,
      "text": "Lush bush that merges from foothills into fertile farmland,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28359.0,
      "end_time": 32637.0,
      "text": "cut through by pristine rivers that snake down from the alps above."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33100.0,
      "end_time": 36430.0,
      "text": "And a lake that sparkles like polished glass"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36437.0,
      "end_time": 39000.0,
      "text": "while the rainbows write color in the sky."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40588.0,
      "end_time": 43318.0,
      "text": "I grew up in the Gloriavale Christian Community."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 44292.0,
      "end_time": 46639.0,
      "text": "Five hundred men, women, and children"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46640.0,
      "end_time": 49642.0,
      "text": "living together and following the doctrines of Jesus Christ."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 50471.0,
      "end_time": 52260.0,
      "text": "My grandfather was my hero"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52261.0,
      "end_time": 54321.0,
      "text": "because he brought us to this land"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 54321.0,
      "end_time": 56791.0,
      "text": "and founded the community I loved."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57866.0,
      "end_time": 60357.0,
      "text": "Purchasing the two farms on either side of the river"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 60367.0,
      "end_time": 62320.0,
      "text": "was a smart move for our group."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 62328.0,
      "end_time": 65791.0,
      "text": "We&#39;d migrated from the East coast and needed livelihood."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66424.0,
      "end_time": 70271.0,
      "text": "I arrived at six weeks old, strapped on my papa&#39;s back"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 70828.0,
      "end_time": 74298.0,
      "text": "to what would be home for the first eighteen years of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 75634.0,
      "end_time": 79678.0,
      "text": "My cousins and childhood friends were like brothers and sisters to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 79678.0,
      "end_time": 81467.0,
      "text": "We did everything together."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 81924.0,
      "end_time": 84667.0,
      "text": "Camping was one of our favorite pastimes."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 84670.0,
      "end_time": 87422.0,
      "text": "We snuggled in sleeping bags underneath the stars"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 87422.0,
      "end_time": 90271.0,
      "text": "and cooked damper on campfire ashes."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 91771.0,
      "end_time": 96370.0,
      "text": "Now, earlier today we were asked to recall our happiest childhood memory."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 96719.0,
      "end_time": 99878.0,
      "text": "My favorite is celebration day."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 100483.0,
      "end_time": 104468.0,
      "text": "Imagine the coolest party you ever attended as a child."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 105740.0,
      "end_time": 107960.0,
      "text": "My cousins, my friends, and I"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 107960.0,
      "end_time": 113890.0,
      "text": "would gorge ourselves on pink candy floss and drink way too much sugary soda."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 113670.0,
      "end_time": 115711.0,
      "text": "There were clowns on stilts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 115711.0,
      "end_time": 117601.0,
      "text": "back-rides behind tractors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 117601.0,
      "end_time": 118731.0,
      "text": "three-legged races,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 118731.0,
      "end_time": 123780.0,
      "text": "and a plane that flew over to drop lollies from the sky."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 125410.0,
      "end_time": 129380.0,
      "text": "The men built us a hydro slide and a flying fox."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 129657.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130982.00000000001,
      "text": "And on these days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 130982.0,
      "end_time": 135571.0,
      "text": "my granddad would decree a day off work for the entire community."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 136230.0,
      "end_time": 138293.0,
      "text": "So the women stopped working in the kitchen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 138293.0,
      "end_time": 140795.0,
      "text": "and the men came, enough to form a festival."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 141335.0,
      "end_time": 143478.0,
      "text": "And it was all free."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 144118.0,
      "end_time": 147506.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t pay for it, because we didn&#39;t earn wages."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 148350.0,
      "end_time": 149900.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t work for money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 150354.0,
      "end_time": 152341.0,
      "text": "we worked for the lifestyle"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 152341.0,
      "end_time": 153901.0,
      "text": "and for each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 154894.0,
      "end_time": 158955.0,
      "text": "The money we made in our businesses was kept in a communal bank account."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 159491.0,
      "end_time": 163217.0,
      "text": "That bank account built the hostels we lived in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 163217.0,
      "end_time": 164918.0,
      "text": "put clothes on our back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 164919.0,
      "end_time": 166615.0,
      "text": "and food in our mouths."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 167836.0,
      "end_time": 171921.0,
      "text": "And I knew every single person in my community personally."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 172227.0,
      "end_time": 174890.0,
      "text": "Not only did I know them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 174890.0,
      "end_time": 175963.0,
      "text": "but I knew their husband,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 175963.0,
      "end_time": 178733.0,
      "text": "their wife, their children and their grandchildren."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 179293.0,
      "end_time": 181218.0,
      "text": "We lived in communal hostels."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 181697.0,
      "end_time": 182943.0,
      "text": "We worked together."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 182943.0,
      "end_time": 184643.0,
      "text": "We went to school together."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 184643.0,
      "end_time": 186243.0,
      "text": "We prayed together."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 186604.0,
      "end_time": 191119.0,
      "text": "I was constantly surrounded by the people I loved the most."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 191690.0,
      "end_time": 194748.0,
      "text": "And at night, I&#39;d skip a couple of meters to my cousin&#39;s room"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 194752.0,
      "end_time": 197601.0,
      "text": "to socialize or play a deck of cards."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 197601.0,
      "end_time": 200661.0,
      "text": "I loved working with the other girls in the women&#39;s realm."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 200661.0,
      "end_time": 205611.0,
      "text": "I loved learning the sew, knit, spin, and cook."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 206779.0,
      "end_time": 209558.0,
      "text": "Music was one of my favorite hobbies."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 209930.0,
      "end_time": 212251.0,
      "text": "We were taught music in the first year of school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 212253.0,
      "end_time": 214107.0,
      "text": "so by the time I was 17,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 214548.0,
      "end_time": 218172.0,
      "text": "I was competent on five musical instruments."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 219655.0,
      "end_time": 225727.0,
      "text": "Think for a moment about a time you achieved something really important."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 226673.0,
      "end_time": 228614.0,
      "text": "Remember how it felt."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 229860.0,
      "end_time": 232224.0,
      "text": "Remember how proud you were in the moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 233870.0,
      "end_time": 237870.0,
      "text": "That probably felt similar to the day I received my first school report."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 237870.0,
      "end_time": 241748.0,
      "text": "It was the most exciting day of my life as a six-year-old."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 242190.0,
      "end_time": 243909.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d scored excellent grades"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 243909.0,
      "end_time": 247369.0,
      "text": "and even better personal comments from my school teacher."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 248247.0,
      "end_time": 252166.0,
      "text": "So you can imagine my excitement when my grandfather took the school report"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 252796.0,
      "end_time": 257281.0,
      "text": "and read it to the 500 members of my community at dinner."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 257901.0,
      "end_time": 262462.0,
      "text": "And then he said, \"We don&#39;t want women like you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 263372.0,
      "end_time": 265260.0,
      "text": "My stomach dropped."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 265540.0,
      "end_time": 267960.0,
      "text": "I turned bright red."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 268576.0,
      "end_time": 271206.0,
      "text": "There was air being sucked in my nostrils,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 272600.0,
      "end_time": 273895.0,
      "text": "but I couldn&#39;t breathe."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 275955.0,
      "end_time": 280102.0,
      "text": "See, my school teacher had written in my report a sentence that read,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 280928.0,
      "end_time": 283959.0,
      "text": "\"Lilia demonstrates leadership skills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 284320.0,
      "end_time": 287372.0,
      "text": "which could be useful for when she&#39;s older.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 288636.0,
      "end_time": 292489.0,
      "text": "And my grandfather humiliated me for hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 293292.0,
      "end_time": 297589.0,
      "text": "And this would become a common theme throughout my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 300323.0,
      "end_time": 304604.0,
      "text": "Afterward, I left the dinning room a changed six-year-old girl."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 306255.0,
      "end_time": 308415.0,
      "text": "And what changed was my belief"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 308415.0,
      "end_time": 312415.0,
      "text": "I was worth anything more than what he sees I was."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 317500.0,
      "end_time": 318112.0,
      "text": "And as a young girl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 318112.0,
      "end_time": 320763.0,
      "text": "I spent the majority of my time with womenfolk."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 321464.0,
      "end_time": 324782.0,
      "text": "And because we home-birthed big families,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 324782.0,
      "end_time": 328782.0,
      "text": "the sight of a pregnant belly made me feel at home."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 330170.0,
      "end_time": 333420.0,
      "text": "My mum grew up with 15 brothers and sisters."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 334760.0,
      "end_time": 336560.0,
      "text": "I have nine siblings."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 338693.0,
      "end_time": 340258.0,
      "text": "I was seven years old"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 340677.0,
      "end_time": 343750.0,
      "text": "when I saw a newborn baby for the first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 344589.0,
      "end_time": 348957.0,
      "text": "I took a scissors with both hands and snipped the umbilical cord."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 350610.0,
      "end_time": 354848.0,
      "text": "My cousin was born blue because the cord was strangling him."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 355713.0,
      "end_time": 357211.0,
      "text": "So after saving him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 357514.0,
      "end_time": 359661.0,
      "text": "the midwife did a trauma assessment with me"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 359661.0,
      "end_time": 362981.0,
      "text": "because I was 10 years old at the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 363834.0,
      "end_time": 367970.0,
      "text": "And I held my aunt&#39;s hand when her next girl was delivered"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 368444.0,
      "end_time": 373588.0,
      "text": "on a mattress in the back of a van, on the way to the nearest hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 375391.0,
      "end_time": 378476.0,
      "text": "Dad was the active manager for one of the businesses."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 378791.0,
      "end_time": 380940.0,
      "text": "My mum was the leader of all the women"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 380941.0,
      "end_time": 384131.0,
      "text": "and ran the entire domestic realm of Gloriavale."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 384522.0,
      "end_time": 387899.0,
      "text": "I wanted to be just like her when I grew up."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 388610.0,
      "end_time": 389718.0,
      "text": "Her job was demanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 389723.0,
      "end_time": 392492.0,
      "text": "and because Dad was often travelling for business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 393120.0,
      "end_time": 395157.0,
      "text": "she needed help raising the children."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 395777.0,
      "end_time": 398467.0,
      "text": "So I changed dirty nappies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 398467.0,
      "end_time": 399738.0,
      "text": "potty-trained,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 399738.0,
      "end_time": 401848.0,
      "text": "climbed out of bed in the middle of the night"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 401848.0,
      "end_time": 403418.0,
      "text": "to rock them back to sleep,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 404666.0,
      "end_time": 406123.0,
      "text": "cleaned up spew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 407429.0,
      "end_time": 409573.0,
      "text": "knitted them warm clothes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 410683.0,
      "end_time": 413492.0,
      "text": "and helped wean them off breast milk."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 414321.0,
      "end_time": 418454.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t wait to grow up and marry a man"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 418717.0,
      "end_time": 420405.0,
      "text": "and have his babies."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 421598.0,
      "end_time": 423978.0,
      "text": "My girl cousin and I talked about it a lot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 423979.0,
      "end_time": 427330.0,
      "text": "so it was a really exciting day for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 427330.0,
      "end_time": 431121.0,
      "text": "when I turned twelve and got my period."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 432204.0,
      "end_time": 436633.0,
      "text": "Because I could finally fulfill my purpose in life."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 438351.0,
      "end_time": 440171.0,
      "text": "And by the time I was 14,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 440592.0,
      "end_time": 443546.0,
      "text": "I knew who I wanted to fulfill that purpose with."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 444569.0,
      "end_time": 446231.0,
      "text": "His name was Willing."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 447723.0,
      "end_time": 450450.0,
      "text": "It would be a worthy marriage."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 450480.0,
      "end_time": 453958.0,
      "text": "I was the granddaughter of the church founder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 453965.0,
      "end_time": 458193.0,
      "text": "and he was the son of Fervent, one of the church leaders."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 460686.0,
      "end_time": 462876.0,
      "text": "And one day I was sitting in class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 463837.0,
      "end_time": 467389.0,
      "text": "when Fervent bowled in the door, dragging Willing by the shoulder."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 470450.0,
      "end_time": 472280.0,
      "text": "Willing had been disobedient."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 473490.0,
      "end_time": 474578.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t remember what he&#39;d done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 474579.0,
      "end_time": 477799.0,
      "text": "it could have been that he combed his hair the wrong way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 477803.0,
      "end_time": 479543.0,
      "text": "spoke back to his father,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 479543.0,
      "end_time": 482723.0,
      "text": "listened to music he wasn&#39;t allowed to listen to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 482724.0,
      "end_time": 484960.0,
      "text": "or read a book he wasn&#39;t allowed to read."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 485454.0,
      "end_time": 486939.0,
      "text": "That didn&#39;t matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 486942.0,
      "end_time": 489688.0,
      "text": "The punishment was the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 492720.0,
      "end_time": 497773.0,
      "text": "Willing was ordered to bend over and pull down his pants."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 498679.0,
      "end_time": 500859.0,
      "text": "And my stomach rolled"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 500859.0,
      "end_time": 503279.0,
      "text": "when Fervent pulled out the leather belt."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 505667.0,
      "end_time": 508671.0,
      "text": "We were then told to watch"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 509622.0,
      "end_time": 512220.0,
      "text": "as Fervent beat Willing with it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 512953.0,
      "end_time": 514803.0,
      "text": "and I refused to look;"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 514803.0,
      "end_time": 520523.0,
      "text": "instead, I stared down at my desk and whispered, \"Please God, make it stop.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 520523.0,
      "end_time": 523180.0,
      "text": "Please make it stop."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 526750.0,
      "end_time": 527452.0,
      "text": "In that moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 527817.0,
      "end_time": 530623.0,
      "text": "my respect for Fervent&#39;s leadership"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 530623.0,
      "end_time": 532230.0,
      "text": "imploded."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 532319.0,
      "end_time": 535189.0,
      "text": "I knew what he was doing was wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 536261.0,
      "end_time": 539752.0,
      "text": "They taught us so much about the love of God"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 540543.0,
      "end_time": 543268.0,
      "text": "that as I watched Fervent beat his son,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 543573.0,
      "end_time": 545836.0,
      "text": "I thought that&#39;s not love."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 546421.0,
      "end_time": 548491.0,
      "text": "And it wasn&#39;t love"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 549120.0,
      "end_time": 553230.0,
      "text": "even though after Fervent had finished beating his son,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 553362.0,
      "end_time": 556934.0,
      "text": "he hugged him and told him he loved him."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 557895.0,
      "end_time": 559425.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s not love."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 561637.0,
      "end_time": 565637.0,
      "text": "I became suspicious of the laws we were being taught."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 566425.0,
      "end_time": 570579.0,
      "text": "\"Spare the rod, spoil the child,\" the leaders said."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 571332.0,
      "end_time": 576420.0,
      "text": "My blood boiled when one wife brought her child to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 576420.0,
      "end_time": 579403.0,
      "text": "and showed me the blue welt on the toddler&#39;s back."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 580770.0,
      "end_time": 582120.0,
      "text": "I gritted my teeth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 582120.0,
      "end_time": 585892.0,
      "text": "\"How can anyone call themselves a Christian"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 586282.0,
      "end_time": 588530.0,
      "text": "and treat a child that way?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 589562.0,
      "end_time": 593662.0,
      "text": "\"How can any parent treat a child that way?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 595582.0,
      "end_time": 599720.0,
      "text": "My friend Jubilant wasn&#39;t spoiled."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 599452.0,
      "end_time": 603562.0,
      "text": "He was born into one of the least privileged families in our society"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 603562.0,
      "end_time": 606792.0,
      "text": "with no connection to leadership circles."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 608316.0,
      "end_time": 610602.0,
      "text": "He was the jokester of our class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 610602.0,
      "end_time": 613842.0,
      "text": "always saying witty things to make us laugh."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 615134.0,
      "end_time": 616330.0,
      "text": "Imagine"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 616794.0,
      "end_time": 618330.0,
      "text": "your brother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 618342.0,
      "end_time": 619901.0,
      "text": "one of your children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 620893.0,
      "end_time": 623580.0,
      "text": "your nephew and niece,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 623640.0,
      "end_time": 624583.0,
      "text": "your daughter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 624583.0,
      "end_time": 627793.0,
      "text": "the one who makes everyone laugh,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 627793.0,
      "end_time": 629123.0,
      "text": "the clown,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 629603.0,
      "end_time": 631122.0,
      "text": "that was Jubilant."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 632487.0,
      "end_time": 633796.0,
      "text": "And one day at soccer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 634486.0,
      "end_time": 637216.0,
      "text": "Jubilant made one too many jokes."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 638543.0,
      "end_time": 643603.0,
      "text": "And when our teacher Nathaniel began to punch and kick him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 643609.0,
      "end_time": 645950.0,
      "text": "my stomach rolled again."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 646993.0,
      "end_time": 648433.0,
      "text": "The game froze,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 648445.0,
      "end_time": 650733.0,
      "text": "and we looked on horrified,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 650733.0,
      "end_time": 654478.0,
      "text": "and I thought Nathaniel would stop."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 655803.0,
      "end_time": 657218.0,
      "text": "But he didn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 657569.0,
      "end_time": 659708.0,
      "text": "He forced Jubilant to walk"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 660550.0,
      "end_time": 662868.0,
      "text": "from the soccer field to the main building,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 663519.0,
      "end_time": 667519.0,
      "text": "all the while punching and kicking him."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 667970.0,
      "end_time": 670900.0,
      "text": "And Jubilant was sobbing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 670900.0,
      "end_time": 673699.0,
      "text": "raising his hands to shield his head from the blows."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 674647.0,
      "end_time": 675847.0,
      "text": "And I thought"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 675847.0,
      "end_time": 679293.0,
      "text": "surely Nathaniel would be dismissed as our school teacher."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 680225.0,
      "end_time": 683893.0,
      "text": "But the next day, he was back in the classroom with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 685179.0,
      "end_time": 686139.0,
      "text": "And I thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 686139.0,
      "end_time": 689259.0,
      "text": "\"What&#39;s wrong with the people running this place?"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 689859.0,
      "end_time": 692690.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t want to have children here.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 699300.0,
      "end_time": 703719.0,
      "text": "Not wanting children was a sin that was forbidden."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 705109.0,
      "end_time": 708173.0,
      "text": "My best friend Grace was an unwanted child."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 708892.0,
      "end_time": 710681.0,
      "text": "Her mother had given her up at birth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 710685.0,
      "end_time": 714930.0,
      "text": "and her adoptive parents shipped her from the U.S to our community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 714930.0,
      "end_time": 718489.0,
      "text": "hoping that good influence would set her straight."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 722987.0,
      "end_time": 724327.0,
      "text": "Excuse me."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 725980.0,
      "end_time": 728795.0,
      "text": "She was a chocolate-skinned Mexican girl"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 729285.0,
      "end_time": 732430.0,
      "text": "who arrived in Gloriavale when she was 13,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 732745.0,
      "end_time": 735368.0,
      "text": "just three years older than me."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 735783.0,
      "end_time": 738813.0,
      "text": "I loved that girl more than life."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 739210.0,
      "end_time": 742750.0,
      "text": "She giggled lots and made me fell safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 742750.0,
      "end_time": 744369.0,
      "text": "So we became best friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 744369.0,
      "end_time": 747290.0,
      "text": "and spent as many moments as we could together."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 748969.0,
      "end_time": 753490.0,
      "text": "And Grace brought personal possessions from the outside world:"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 753490.0,
      "end_time": 754189.0,
      "text": "music,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 754189.0,
      "end_time": 755169.0,
      "text": "jewelry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 755169.0,
      "end_time": 756126.0,
      "text": "makeup."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 757111.0,
      "end_time": 758670.0,
      "text": "These were forbidden."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 758912.0,
      "end_time": 763222.0,
      "text": "And seeing them for the first time made Grace all the more special in my eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 763543.0,
      "end_time": 766278.0,
      "text": "Her rebellious spirit inspired me."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 766929.0,
      "end_time": 768757.0,
      "text": "And over the years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 768758.0,
      "end_time": 771554.0,
      "text": "Grace would be punished many times"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 771895.0,
      "end_time": 774648.0,
      "text": "because she refused to be controlled."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 776990.0,
      "end_time": 779880.0,
      "text": "She was 20 when she came to me and told me"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 779880.0,
      "end_time": 784280.0,
      "text": "the leaders had ordered her marriage to a man she didn&#39;t love."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 785932.0,
      "end_time": 787368.0,
      "text": "She was sobbing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 787850.0,
      "end_time": 788940.0,
      "text": "trembling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 789615.0,
      "end_time": 792135.0,
      "text": "tears were streaming down her cheeks."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 793810.0,
      "end_time": 795331.0,
      "text": "In desperation, she&#39;d packed her bags,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 795331.0,
      "end_time": 796791.0,
      "text": "hidden them under a tree,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 796791.0,
      "end_time": 799780.0,
      "text": "called a friend on the outside to come rescue her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 799430.0,
      "end_time": 801911.0,
      "text": "but she was discovered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 802528.0,
      "end_time": 807838.0,
      "text": "taken before an inquisition of 20 men seated in a small room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 808131.0,
      "end_time": 809548.0,
      "text": "condemned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 809998.0,
      "end_time": 812288.0,
      "text": "forced to confess she was evil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 813248.0,
      "end_time": 817504.0,
      "text": "forced to phone her outside family and say she didn&#39;t want to leave anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 818560.0,
      "end_time": 819979.0,
      "text": "And I thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 820580.0,
      "end_time": 822360.0,
      "text": "\"Fuck them."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 823800.0,
      "end_time": 826218.0,
      "text": "No one tells my best friend what to do.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 827473.0,
      "end_time": 830152.0,
      "text": "So I wrapped my arms around her and I said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 830484.0,
      "end_time": 832900.0,
      "text": "\"Don&#39;t listen to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 832928.0,
      "end_time": 836629.0,
      "text": "You do what you believe is right.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 838266.0,
      "end_time": 839397.0,
      "text": "Thankfully,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 839406.0,
      "end_time": 841694.0,
      "text": "her adoptive parents came through."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 842532.0,
      "end_time": 844670.0,
      "text": "They phoned Gloriavale"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 844740.0,
      "end_time": 848742.0,
      "text": "and threatened to send in the police if Grace wasn&#39;t allowed to leave."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 849533.0,
      "end_time": 851603.0,
      "text": "The next day, she was gone."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 852588.0,
      "end_time": 856300.0,
      "text": "And she now lives happily in Canada."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 859605.0,
      "end_time": 860835.0,
      "text": "Excuse me."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 862684.0,
      "end_time": 864872.0,
      "text": "After the incident with Grace,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 865445.0,
      "end_time": 867894.0,
      "text": "I knew I had to leave too,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 868489.0,
      "end_time": 871999.0,
      "text": "or I would be forced to marry a man I didn&#39;t love."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 873395.0,
      "end_time": 877603.0,
      "text": "And I knew I had to take my little sisters with me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 877603.0,
      "end_time": 880853.0,
      "text": "or the same thing would happen to them."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 882380.0,
      "end_time": 884960.0,
      "text": "I had one foot out the door already."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 886124.0,
      "end_time": 887979.0,
      "text": "When I was 11,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 887979.0,
      "end_time": 891354.0,
      "text": "my oldest sibling ran away."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 892192.0,
      "end_time": 893652.0,
      "text": "When I was 13,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 893652.0,
      "end_time": 896662.0,
      "text": "my next oldest sibling ran away."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 897469.0,
      "end_time": 899590.0,
      "text": "When I was 17,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 899590.0,
      "end_time": 901449.0,
      "text": "my younger brother threatened to leave."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 902366.0,
      "end_time": 906468.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t know it at the time, but my parents were ready to leave too."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 907880.0,
      "end_time": 910817.0,
      "text": "But they couldn&#39;t bear the thought of losing another child."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 912226.0,
      "end_time": 916226.0,
      "text": "They were waiting for me to come around so we could stay together."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 920616.0,
      "end_time": 922586.0,
      "text": "After what happened to Grace,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 923148.0,
      "end_time": 924918.0,
      "text": "I was ready to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 927318.0,
      "end_time": 932428.0,
      "text": "I left Gloriavale with my entire family less than a year after Grace had."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 936980.0,
      "end_time": 938137.0,
      "text": "And after I left the cult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 938137.0,
      "end_time": 942160.0,
      "text": "I became obsessed with learning everything I could about human behavior"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 942287.0,
      "end_time": 946137.0,
      "text": "because I thought, \"If I can understand myself and others better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 946502.0,
      "end_time": 948541.0,
      "text": "I can protect myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 949319.0,
      "end_time": 953319.0,
      "text": "I can make sure no one ever takes advantage of me ever again.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 955521.0,
      "end_time": 960314.0,
      "text": "And as I wrote the story of my life in a religious cult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 960636.0,
      "end_time": 963271.0,
      "text": "I realized the leaders of Gloriavale"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 963272.0,
      "end_time": 967906.0,
      "text": "used cruel tactics to control and manipulate me."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 968856.0,
      "end_time": 971286.0,
      "text": "They began by using shame"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 971286.0,
      "end_time": 974260.0,
      "text": "to degrade me in front of the people I loved."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 975700.0,
      "end_time": 978450.0,
      "text": "It started with my grandfather publicly disgracing me"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 978875.0,
      "end_time": 981600.0,
      "text": "for my six-year-old report card."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 981574.0,
      "end_time": 984964.0,
      "text": "His action sends a clear message of who&#39;s in charge."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 985265.0,
      "end_time": 989265.0,
      "text": "We all knew what would happen to people who dared Christian authority."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 990826.0,
      "end_time": 992216.0,
      "text": "But it didn&#39;t end there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 992216.0,
      "end_time": 997228.0,
      "text": "they began using guilt to degrade my self-worth."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 997798.0,
      "end_time": 1000823.0,
      "text": "When I was a child, they told me every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 1001220.0,
      "end_time": 1003296.0,
      "text": "I was a worthless sinner."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 1003870.0,
      "end_time": 1005550.0,
      "text": "It was my fault."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 1005930.0,
      "end_time": 1007239.0,
      "text": "I was evil."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 1007240.0,
      "end_time": 1008989.0,
      "text": "I was the one to blame."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 1009310.0,
      "end_time": 1013407.0,
      "text": "When people treated me badly I thought I deserved it."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 1014530.0,
      "end_time": 1016363.0,
      "text": "I struggled to think correct for myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 1016360.0,
      "end_time": 1018430.0,
      "text": "because I was always second-guessing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 1018430.0,
      "end_time": 1020160.0,
      "text": "What if it is my fault?"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 1020950.0,
      "end_time": 1022420.0,
      "text": "What if I am to blame?"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 1024339.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1026801.9999999999,
      "text": "Now, they may have beaten me down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 1026810.0,
      "end_time": 1030580.0,
      "text": "but they messed up when they mistreated the people I loved."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 1032540.0,
      "end_time": 1039175.0,
      "text": "My fury towards the injustices suffered by Grace, Jubilant, and Willing"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 1039550.0,
      "end_time": 1043361.0,
      "text": "gave me the strength I hadn&#39;t been able to muster for myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 1044359.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1048526.9999999999,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t stand by and watch someone I loved wrongly suffer."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 1049760.0,
      "end_time": 1054368.0,
      "text": "Love for others broke the chains that shackled me."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 1056320.0,
      "end_time": 1060320.0,
      "text": "But why was I willing to love them and not myself?"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 1061850.0,
      "end_time": 1064234.0,
      "text": "Eventually, I realized that if ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 1065370.0,
      "end_time": 1067848.0,
      "text": "I could learn to love myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 1068140.0,
      "end_time": 1070144.0,
      "text": "the way I loved Willing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 1070150.0,
      "end_time": 1072550.0,
      "text": "the way I love Jubilant and Grace,"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 1072550.0,
      "end_time": 1075386.0,
      "text": "the way I love my little sisters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 1075850.0,
      "end_time": 1078395.0,
      "text": "then I wouldn&#39;t take anyone&#39;s bullshit."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 1079130.0,
      "end_time": 1080352.0,
      "text": "So I asked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 1080980.0,
      "end_time": 1083760.0,
      "text": "What does it mean to love myself?"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 1084670.0,
      "end_time": 1088374.0,
      "text": "What does it mean to love myself so fully"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 1088580.0,
      "end_time": 1091702.0,
      "text": "that if anyone ever tries to shame me again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 1091700.0,
      "end_time": 1094810.0,
      "text": "I am the first to stand up for myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 1096960.0,
      "end_time": 1100110.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t have all the answers, but I&#39;ve come a long way."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 1100530.0,
      "end_time": 1102100.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ve come to realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 1102100.0,
      "end_time": 1105560.0,
      "text": "that my six-year-old report card was bang-on."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 1106180.0,
      "end_time": 1108300.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 1108300.0,
      "end_time": 1111450.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 1119870.0,
      "end_time": 1123271.0,
      "text": "And my grandfather was terrified of strong women."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 1123270.0,
      "end_time": 1125496.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 1125500.0,
      "end_time": 1127316.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a strong woman."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 1127320.0,
      "end_time": 1129787.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a leader."
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 1129490.0,
      "end_time": 1130576.0,
      "text": "Today I know"
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 1130580.0,
      "end_time": 1133179.0,
      "text": "my leadership skills are priceless."
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 1135780.0,
      "end_time": 1137571.0,
      "text": "I used them to leave the church"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 1137570.0,
      "end_time": 1140739.0,
      "text": "and find my own way in the world that, honestly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 1141210.0,
      "end_time": 1145210.0,
      "text": "still scares the living hell out of me."
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 1146560.0,
      "end_time": 1149530.0,
      "text": "I used them when I was 23 to run a business"
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 1150150.0,
      "end_time": 1154418.0,
      "text": "and to write a book that teaches others what&#39;s possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 1155160.0,
      "end_time": 1157410.0,
      "text": "Now at 27 years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 1157410.0,
      "end_time": 1160650.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m using them to stand here with you today."
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 1161510.0,
      "end_time": 1165740.0,
      "text": "I use them every day to remind my six-year-old self"
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 1166680.0,
      "end_time": 1169480.0,
      "text": "she can do anything she wants to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 328,
      "start_time": 1169410.0,
      "end_time": 1173248.0,
      "text": "and to never let anyone tell her otherwise."
    },
    {
      "index": 329,
      "start_time": 1174530.0,
      "end_time": 1175639.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 330,
      "start_time": 1175640.0,
      "end_time": 1180552.0,
      "text": "(Applause) (Cheers)"
    }
  ]
}